      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <p>The Albert M. Greenfield <%= link_to "SCRC", webpages_scrc_path %> Reading Room’s hours can be verified prior to your visit by viewing the <%= link_to "library hours page", hours_path %>, or the box at the bottom of this page. </p>
      </div>
